<item>
            <title>[SOLR-501] /admin/analysis.jsp does not decode input string as UTF-8 sequence.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-501</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In servlet2.5, we should call HttpRequestServlet.setCharacterEncoding(&quot;UTF-8&quot;) to get a UTF-8 character sequence via request.getParameter() in JSP.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Tomcat6.0&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12390461">SOLR-501</key>
            <summary>/admin/analysis.jsp does not decode input string as UTF-8 sequence.</summary>
